Project name: pan-genome pipeline_part1
Version: 1.0
Require:
    g++(version>7.5.0, to be able to use regex)
    c++(version:17,to be able to use file manage lib)
    zlib
    alignment tools available in path
Version feature:
    1.Multi thread safe.
    2.All the parameters is accessible outside the program.
Developer: kongshuang
Warning:
    1.Before running the pipeline, you have to make sure all the program is available in your current envrionment.
    2.All the parameter associated with corresponding process is accessible in the configfile. Changing of paramter's format is not allowed! or you will get an error!
    3.Thread could be controled by several Thread option in configfile, but be careful when the process has thread option itself.
    4.To be able to use regex, please install new version of g++(version 7.5.0 works fine for me), or the program will not compile successful.

